Sentencas: A novel low-temperature sealing method was developed to seal solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: The 3D Ni nanosheet array was pre-fabricated on faying surfaces of Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode-support.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: Then it was covered with Au film without changing its morphology.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: This special nanostructure improved sintering efficiency between Ag nano particles and substrates.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: A dense joint was obtained at the low-temperature between 250 degrees C-300 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: This method effectively avoided the oxidation of interconnect during sealing.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: When joints were sealed at 300 degrees C, the shear strength reached 16 MPa.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: The fracture was mainly located in the central Ag layer, presenting a significant plastic deformation.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: Due to the effective protection of Ni layer, joints also possessed excellent oxidation resistance in oxidizing atmosphere at 800 C for 400 h. After high-temperature oxidation, the shear strength was increased to 23 MPa, revealing an increasement of 43.8% compared with the as-sealed condition (16 MPa).
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: This sealing method has great potential in sealing solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of 3D Hi nanosheet array on Crofer22APU interconnect and NiO-YSZ anode support to sinter with small-size Ag nanoparticles for low-temperature sealing SOFCs

Sentencas: It also can be extended to seal other energy-conversion devices.
